<td class="navbox-group" style=";padding:0.35em 1.0em; line-height:1.2em;;">Writings</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<div>
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Novels:</b> <i><a href="/wiki/The_Caves_of_Steel" title="The Caves of Steel">The Caves of Steel</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Naked_Sun" title="The Naked Sun">The Naked Sun</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Robots_of_Dawn" title="The Robots of Dawn">The Robots of Dawn</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Robots_and_Empire" title="Robots and Empire">Robots and Empire</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Positronic_Man" title="The Positronic Man">The Positronic Man</a></i></span><br />
<span style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Short story collections:</b> <i><a href="/wiki/I,_Robot" title="I, Robot">I, Robot</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Rest_of_the_Robots" title="The Rest of the Robots">The Rest of the Robots</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Complete_Robot" title="The Complete Robot">The Complete Robot</a></i> &#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Robot_Dreams" title="Robot Dreams">Robot Dreams</a></i> &#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Robot_Visions" title="Robot Visions">Robot Visions</a></i></span><br />
<b>Second Robot series</b> (by <a href="/wiki/Roger_McBride_Allen" title="Roger McBride Allen" class="mw-redirect">Roger McBride Allen</a>)<b>:</b> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Isaac_Asimov%27s_Caliban" title="Isaac Asimov's Caliban">Isaac Asimov's Caliban</a></i> &#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Isaac_Asimov%27s_Inferno" title="Isaac Asimov's Inferno">Isaac Asimov's Inferno</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Isaac_Asimov%27s_Utopia" title="Isaac Asimov's Utopia">Isaac Asimov's Utopia</a></i></span><br />
<span style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Robot Mystery series</b> (by <a href="/wiki/Mark_W._Tiedemann" title="Mark W. Tiedemann">Mark W. Tiedemann</a> and <a href="/wiki/Alexander_C._Irvine" title="Alexander C. Irvine">Alexander C. Irvine</a>)<b>:</b> <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mirage_(novel)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Mirage (novel) (page does not exist)">Mirage</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Chimera_(Tiedemann_novel)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Chimera (Tiedemann novel) (page does not exist)">Chimera</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Aurora_(novel)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Aurora (novel) (page does not exist)">Aurora</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Have_Robot,_Will_Travel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Have Robot, Will Travel (page does not exist)">Have Robot, Will Travel</a></i></span></p>
